The end-use segment further highlights the versatility of camping tents, with applications ranging from recreational activities to military and civil purposes. Recreational campers seek tents that offer comfort, durability, and convenience during camping trips, emphasizing the importance of quality and performance-driven features. Military and civil end-users require specialized tents designed for specific operational requirements, such as field deployments or emergency response situations, showcasing the adaptable nature of camping tent products in various contexts.

